Quickstrike:





Quickstrike turned his head, half asleep, noticing Stringtra exiting the CR 
chamber. He heard her say something about going out scouting.

He snapped harshly at her, "Scoutin'? Did ya day ya were goin' out scoutin'? 
Ya ain't goin' no where! We're th' only ones here! Ya stay here and stay 
put!" He shook his head. "Ah'm tired. Ah'm goin' to sleep. Keep watch!" He 
walked to the side of the cave, close to the mouth of the cave. He 
transformed to beast mode and tucked his claws in, and lowered his body.
